OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FFinal day of trains on     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fmajor line until 2024      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Passengers on a major commuter line    
OL,6, will not be able to catch a train until
OL,7, 2024 as upgrade work is about to begin.
OL,9,FFrom Sunday, the line from Treherbert  
OL,10,Fto Pontypridd in Rhondda Cynon Taf will
OL,11,Fclose and replacement buses introduced.
OL,13,FThe work is part of the shift to the   
OL,14,FSouth Wales Metro, which is now #260m  
OL,15,Fover budget at #1bn.                   
OL,17,FTransport Minister Lee Waters said the 
OL,18,Fdisruption would be "worth it", but one
OL,19,FNHS worker said replacement buses set  
OL,20,Foff too late for his job.              
